    <h2>Subscription & billing</h2>
    <p>theStacc is a monthly or annual subscription. The price for your plan is shown on the pricing page and on the checkout screen before you pay. Stripe processes every transaction.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Monthly plans</strong> renew on the same day every month. The first charge happens the day you sign up.</li>
